title: Start
body:
<< nametag alex >> 
what an exotic creature!
<< nametag lumina >>
hey that's rude! i am lumina a desert fairy.
<< nametag alex  >>
you even can talk and have name!? wonderful.
<< nametag lumina >>
of course i have a name. by the way what is your purpose in coming to this sacred pyramid ? stealing artifact? you have no difference than the others.
<< nametag alex >>
really? well you'll see about that.
<< nametag lumina >>
how arrogant. you will face a few obstacle along this journey, are you sure?
<< nametag alex >>
yes of course.
<< nametag lumina >>
okay i'll follow along.
